1.body: Levis is Kubernetes Manifest Generator for simply creating Kubernetes applications. Levis generates pure Kubernetes YAML - you can use Levis to define Kubernetes applications with YAML syntax for any Kubernetes clusters running anywhere. This is an project built with ❤️ by KubeOps Skills . We encourage you to try it out , leave feedback , and jump in to help !
1.title: Kubernetes Manifest Generator (with node.js 14)
